commentTextItems.html: short of length hammered over mid on boundary! gets to his 50 in style

commentPostTextItems.html: And that is of course a win for West Indies, in style
Victory to West Indies by 6 wickets with 6.2 overs to spare
This is a good batting wicket and small ground, you need a competitive score
Credits the younger bowlers, and courtney of course
About Powell, very good striker of the ball
Ricardo Powell gets US$ 500 for the fastest fifty of the day
Man of the match gets USD 2,000
And the man of the match is... Ridley Jacobs for 4 catches and a cameo with the bat in the opening slot
That is it folks, we will back for the next match on 4th September

commentTextItems.html: pitched up, Powell cracks it with a huge swing of his bat way over long on
slow full toss on the legs, played to fine leg
on the stumps, played back to the bowler
